{"type": "article", "id": 8956, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-04-28T08:06:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 2833, "name": "厨具"}, {"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 2212, "name": "鞋"}, {"id": 4568, "name": "T恤"}, {"id": 9442, "name": "Georg Jensen"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 335, "name": "Uniqlo"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405552EKi8h1M63C47sUO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tStar Wars T-shirt by UNIQLO\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t优衣库从 2005 开始举办 UT 设计大奖赛，以优衣库 T 恤为底，鼓励人们在上面进行各式各样的创作。今年正好是大奖赛 10 周年，而经典的《星球大战》第 7 部也将于年底上映。于是，优衣库为今年的大奖赛选定的设计主题便是《星球大战》，从去年 7 月份开始，经过层层评选，从 5218 部参赛作品中最终选出了 22 件。最近这个系列的 T 恤作为优衣库春夏系列的组成部分全面上架，不过只有男装和童装两种，但没关系，女生穿男式 T 恤早就不是什么新鲜事儿了。<a href=\"http://www.uniqlo.com/jp/store/feature/uq/ut/utgp2015/\" target=\"_blank\">这是官方购买链接</a>，在<a href=\"http://uniqlo.tmall.com/p/rd615054.htm\" target=\"_blank\">天猫优衣库旗舰店</a>也可以买到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614053958POspRKNUWG6IgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140540FO0Wl9abxIPYR8oi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140540q3QnhBTeAr4kigNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140541fFXdSTCMzO9DVHmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140541fWZXjK6gYUsuNiv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140542w521UdCMVtTJX34W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140542Kd5wjxN2Af1kPz7S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSlip-On by Converse\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t“Slip-On” 被叫做“一脚蹬”，这大概是这几年最火热的鞋子之一，翻译过来的这个词形象地表明了它便于穿脱，搭配方便地特点，一时成为了众多人的心头好。匡威最近对其旗下经典的 Jack Purcell 进行了一次升级，在原来的基础上加入了 Nike Zoom Air 气垫技术，推出了更新版的“一脚蹬”，有蓝色，白色和黑色三种经典颜色可选。预计在本月内面市，喜欢匡威的大家可以保持关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405435yIc3Re8mXdUVk2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140543FQLEbmCJocO0iD9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405445OMZyWbJ30e79ICk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140545yDfgW54tIFXapb3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140545sdSnHxXtF57L3gUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140545XdHBTgpu7E5lYWLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140546Pumv93o67cqMKwhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tT°RED C7OLED by Romolo Stanco &amp; Marmi Serafini\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这款名为 “T°RED C7OLED” 的灯在米兰设计周“碳纤维与设计”专场进行了展出，它采用了大理石的底座，而灯架则是 88.5 厘米的悬挂长丝碳纤维，长丝碳纤维厚度为 4mm，重量则是 188 克，很好地保持了灯具的动感和平衡，上方装有两个 LED 灯泡，看上去简约而时尚。<a href=\"http://www.spaziotadini.it/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>能看到展会现场的情况。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140546JA2GpoVMRbt9P5Ls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405460THOoAUN1spyhQDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140547ONSork9DgT5Bn7El.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140547XHSkNqLUzlEps5J1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140547VqK2JuzHg7cdkRyw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140548RudoVmbfYzSysr8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614054834ILAfDCaTcdP6Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65525672\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tWooden Bicycle by Jan\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t木制自行车返璞归真，越来越吸引大家的关注。最近，来自捷克的 Jan 自行车公司推出了一款木制框架的自行车，木制框架呈牛油果形状，全部由手工制作，一气呵成，无衔接无缝隙。木制架构的基础上，加入金属等必要的元素，构成我们看到的成品自行车，而木结构在减震能力和舒适度上，都有其他材料不可比的特性。Jan 公司表示，因为全部手工制作，自行车不会批量生产，他们试图以此探索自然材料的更多可能性。这是<a href=\"http://bikejan.com/\" target=\"_blank\">公司主页</a>，可以看到更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140549RhK5iXbM1ow7qVA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140549Lf4syKdY1htiOpe7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140549zKi5sELH2u7cD349.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140550Ad8WeOGhRkiaMLf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405509wRgterQCEliUaYJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140551HQtNZWaYzSolVGPc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140551LEtJbGgRkaM2me7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBarbry for Georg Jensen by Aurélien Barbry\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tAurélien Barbry 为 Georg Jensen 带来了一套厨具产品，其中包含一个不锈钢碗，一款配有橡木塞的玻璃水瓶，还有一款金属丝制作的果篮，以及全部采用橡木制作的刮刀和勺子等。产品在上海设计周期间进行了展出。<a href=\"http://www.georgjensen.com/europe/\" target=\"_blank\">在这里</a>可以买到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614055198gzCsF6rQyuSWAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140552Zudgt4LPnD8FUs3l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140552svP2kFCh6QViEKfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140553BpF4W105TeK8UvlR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405539q8CWUxn530AXP72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140554QBpVwDeuFlY98ZA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405547wv0oBrKp9RqnsPb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}